		 	<title>Apple&#39;s Textbooks For 1-percenters Will Leave Most Children Behind | Fox News</title>
		
		
		
		
		
		
		




<meta name="keywords" content="study,Education,computers,U S,technology,North Carolina,Intelligent Design,no doubt,elementary school,the office,Evolution,hacking,eBook,OS X,public schools" />
